---
/**
 * A side-by-side comparison of 2–3 concepts ("reelt vs virtuelt bilde",
 * "konstruktiv vs destruktiv"). Wrap `<CompareCol>` children; each is a titled
 * card. The grid auto-fits, so 2 or 3 columns sit side by side on desktop and
 * stack on narrow screens — no fixed column count to declare, and no fragile
 * Markdown table that wraps badly on mobile.
 */
---

<div class="compare"><slot /></div>

<style>
  .compare {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(100%, 15rem), 1fr));
    margin-block: var(--space-5);
  }
</style>
